@fleet-gateway @feat-fg-001
Feature: Fleet Gateway shared client and gateway interfaces
  As a fleet operator routing user messages through Jarvis to specialist agents
  I want a shared gateway client library consumed by OpenWebUI and Reachy interfaces
  So that wire envelopes, NATS request-reply, and Graphiti reads behave identically across gateways and remain testable in isolation

  Background:
    Given the Fleet Gateway common module is available
    And Jarvis listens on the agents.command.jarvis topic
    And the Graphiti knowledge graph is reachable on the configured FalkorDB endpoint

